<%- include('partials/header') %>

<main class="about-page">
    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>The Havn Philosophy</h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">Quality ownership, intentional design, and a commitment to the places we call home.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="story-section">
        <div class="container flex-row">
            <div class="story-content">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>A home is the foundation of a well-lived life. At <strong>Havn</strong>, we aren't just a management company; we are property owners invested in the long-term health and beauty of our local neighborhoods.</p>
                <p>We acquired our first properties with a simple goal: to provide spaces where we would be proud to live ourselves. By maintaining 100% ownership of our portfolio, we ensure that every repair, every upgrade, and every tenant interaction meets our exact standards of excellence.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="story-image">
                <div class="image-placeholder">Building for the Future</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="values-section">
        <div class="container grid-4">
            <div class="value-card">
                <h3>Integrity</h3>
                <p>We own the buildings, so we take full responsibility for the experience. No excuses, just results.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <h3>Stewardship</h3>
                <p>We don't wait for things to break. We invest in proactive upgrades to keep our properties at peak quality.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <h3>Simplicity</h3>
                <p>From digital leasing to streamlined maintenance, we’ve removed the friction from modern renting.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <h3>Longevity</h3>
                <p>We build lasting relationships with our tenants and contribute positively to the communities we serve.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>